_sText: fpsb_orbital_marbles This is my entry for the marble track contest. The marbles go fast on my track (the double chevrons are boosts) so there's some luck involved in getting the marbles through the course. 80% of the time they make it but sometimes one will fall off. Just restart in this case. Umm I don't have a video for this. FRAPS is stupid and won't record with a high enough framerate. If someone could help me out with a video I'd be much obliged. All custom stuff is paked into the map.
